{"tid":857834,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 恥笑 Pixel 3 XL 劉海大到可以停飛機","createTime":"2018-10-11T10:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T15:35:52.000Z","uid":59499,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1b38c531369878a307b59a5fed365e05e4bac3cf","tid":857834,"uid":59499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:59:11.000Z","msg":"10月9日晚間， Google Pixel 3、Pixel 3 XL正式發布，由於「驚人」的搖格和價格，以及劉海屏的設計，讓許多原來青睞有加的用戶望而卻步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42324344322433324543242.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F42324344322433324543242.jpg&d=%2FXhWzRbh9n3AG2teqPVqX9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=9f8eb75c\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42324344322433324543242.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n不得不說，Pixel 3 XL 劉海屏的寬度實在有點太寬了。畢竟對於在強調屏佔比的今天，各大手機廠商都希望能夠通過減小劉海的寬度來提升屏佔比，而 Pixel 3 XL 似乎在反其道而行。這一次喜歡搞事的 Samusng 怎會放過機會，Samsung 就在 Twitter 上刊一些幽默的 Post 調侃 Google 的 Pixel 3 巨大的劉海，都可以在上面停一架飛機了(You could land a plane on it)。而一些網友也開心「食花生」，在下面不少 Sam粉留言並表明要選購 Samsung 的手機，官方也熱情回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42342344.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F42342344.jpg&d=%2FXhWzRbh9n3AG2teqPVqX9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e1188d46\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/42342344.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n其實，Samsung 自去年 iPhone X 發布後，一直批評競爭對手，如果自家產品也出現這種問題，豈不是瘋狂打臉？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">班老細係到狗咬狗，你叫班打手情以何堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"fb346bdcfbed5304a261e28e8193c3e00e4e2aa6","tid":857834,"uid":59499,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"10月9日晚間， Google Pixel 3、Pixel 3 XL正式發布，由於「驚人」的搖格和價格，以及劉海屏的設計，讓許多原來青睞有加的用戶望而卻步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-c